Helmut was only a baby when he was left in the Forest of Pahe, an evil place full of beasts where sinners are banished for eternity. Luckily, one magical beast and an exiled swordsman take pity on him and raise him as their own. But with a dark seed growing inside him, Helmut decides to take up the sword to prevent the seed from turning him evil. As Helmut grows stronger, he seeks out the family that abandoned him, but will Helmut end up following his human heart or his beastly instincts?
(Source: Tapas)

In a world where the remnants of civilization depend on the Awakened, humans with special powers, to fend off otherworldly monsters, Kim Sunwoo is forced to survive as a mere guide for the Awakened. Just when he thinks his nightmarish days will never end, he's given a mission to protect one of the few remaining safe cities in exchange for a better life. It is then that a strange voice echoes in his head, and he discovers a power that could change the course of the war against monsters forever. (Source: Tapas)
